entries.title: Thermal Evaporator#1
entries.content: Thermal Evaporator#1 will be DOWN on Monday October 14th and Tuesday 15th for a CHA vacuum controller upgrade. If all goes well the system will be up and running late Tuesday afternoon. Silva 07:46, 10 October 2019 (PDT)

entries.title: Suss Bonder
entries.content: Suss Bonder is DOWN. The vendor installed all the hardware but failed to get the software to work. The vendor will be back sometime next week, the week of the 16th, to complete the repair/upgrade. Silva 15:59, 13 September 2019 (PDT)
